Privacy Policy
ShopPet is dedicated to maintaining the privacy of its users. Personal data collected will be used exclusively to improve user experience. We will not sell or share personal data with third parties without user consent. For additional information, please refer to our privacy policy at [link to privacy policy].

Contributions
We encourage contributions to ShopPet from the community. If you have suggestions, bug reports, or ideas, please open an issue or submit a pull request. All feedback and contributions are valuable and will be reviewed with serious consideration.

Contribution Process
Reporting Issues: Please create an issue in our GitHub repository if you encounter a bug or have a suggestion.
Submitting Changes: To propose changes to the code, fork the repository and submit a pull request detailing the modifications.
Follow Guidelines: Please adhere to our coding guidelines when contributing. This helps to ensure that your changes can be easily integrated into the main project.
Contact
For questions or feedback, please reach out to us via email: support@shoppet.com. We look forward to hearing from you and continuing to enhance the software based on your insights.

Thank you for choosing ShopPet! We hope you enjoy using our software and find it valuable.
